<style>
  .letter-spacing {
    letter-spacing: .2px;
  }

  .liga-off {
  <meta name="assert" content="Test that Tibetan shaping works with ligatures disabled.">
    font-feature-settings: "liga" off;
  }
</style>
<body>
<p>Test passes if the three lines below are identical.</p>
<section class="test" lang="bo">
  <p>རྒྱུ</p>
  <p class="letter-spacing">རྒྱུ</p><meta content="Test that Tibetan shaping works with ligatures disabled." name="assert">
  <p class="liga-off">རྒྱུ</p><body>
